    <newsTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[A Universe Where Kids Learn While Playing]]></Value>
    </newsTitle>
    <newsExcerpt>
      <Value><![CDATA[Discover how the Cow Paradise universe blends play and learning into one magical experience for kids.]]></Value>
    </newsExcerpt>
    <newsBody>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>At Cow Paradise, learning isn't a chore — it's an adventure. Children dive into vibrant tropical islands, befriend the Moo Family characters, and pick up letters, numbers, and life skills along the way.</p><p>Every story, every game, and every short is designed by educators and parents who believe play is the most powerful classroom there is.</p>]]></Value>
    </newsBody>
